            del self.items[name]
        else:
            raise ValueError(f"Item '{name}' not found in cart.")

    def total(self):
        return sum(self.items.values())
```

### Step 7: Run Tests Again
After refactoring, run the tests again to ensure everything still works as expected.

### Step 8: Repeat
